animeTitle: Bishoujo Senshi Sailor Moon Eternal Movie 2
otherNames: Pretty Guardians Sailor Moon Eternal The Movie 2, 劇場版 美少女戦士セーラームーンEternal
synopsis: Bishoujo Senshi Sailor Moon Eternal serves as the fourth installment in Toei Animation's reboot of Naoko Takeuchi's original magical girl manga. The sequel was announced in January 2017 as a part of the franchise's 25th anniversary and later confirmed to be a two-part anime film covering the Dream arc.
